12:["$","section",null,{"children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-chalk tracking-tight mb-8","children":"Genesis NFT Discounts"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-6","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-abyss border border-edge/20 rounded-lg p-8","children":[["$","h4",null,{"className":"font-display text-star text-lg mb-3","children":"NFT Fee Discounts"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-dust text-sm leading-relaxed","children":["Genesis NFT holders receive automatic protocol fee discounts. Holding 1+ NFT grants a ",["$","span",null,{"className":"text-chalk font-semibold","children":"15% base discount"}],", plus ",["$","span",null,{"className":"text-chalk font-semibold","children":"+5% per volume tier"}]," (7 tiers from $10K to $1M+) and ",["$","span",null,{"className":"text-chalk font-semibold","children":"+2% per additional NFT"}],", capped at ",["$","span",null,{"className":"text-chalk font-semibold","children":"50% off"}],". Discounts apply to the treasury portion of fees only — the 0.05% relayer fee is never discounted. Applied on-chain by reading the holder's NFT balance — no claiming or staking required. Treasury NFTs (IDs 1-50) are held by the protocol. Public minters (IDs 51-300) purchase at 1,000 STRK each."]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-abyss border border-edge/20 rounded-lg p-8","children":[["$","h4",null,{"className":"font-display text-star text-lg mb-3","children":"Discount Floors"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-dust text-sm leading-relaxed","children":["Even at the maximum 50% discount, the treasury always receives a minimum fee. For lending settlements, the treasury floor is ",["$","span",null,{"className":"text-chalk font-semibold","children":"10 BPS (0.10%)"}],". For swaps, the treasury floor is ",["$","span",null,{"className":"text-chalk font-semibold","children":"5 BPS (0.05%)"}],". The relayer's 5 BPS is never discounted."]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-abyss border border-edge/20 rounded-lg p-8","children":[["$","h4",null,{"className":"font-display text-star text-lg mb-3","children":"Volume Tiers"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-dust text-sm leading-relaxed","children":["Your cumulative settlement volume is tracked per-address on-chain (only whitelisted tokens count toward volume). Each tier adds ",["$","span",null,{"className":"text-chalk font-semibold","children":"+5%"}]," to your discount: $10K, $25K, $50K, $100K, $250K, $500K, and $1M+."]}]]}]]}]]}]]}]
