]," Genesis NFTs are minted to the protocol treasury at deployment. This is hardcoded in the constructor — not an admin action. Treasury NFTs are held for protocol development: ",["$","span",null,{"className":"text-chalk font-medium","children":"security audits, ecosystem growth, and operational costs"}],"."]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-abyss border border-edge/20 rounded-lg p-8","children":[["$","h4",null,{"className":"font-display text-star text-lg mb-3","children":"Per-Wallet Limit"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-dust text-sm leading-relaxed","children":["Public minting is capped at ",["$","span",null,{"className":"text-chalk font-semibold","children":"5 NFTs per wallet"}],", enforced on-chain via the ",["$","span",null,{"className":"text-chalk font-mono text-xs","children":"MAX_PER_WALLET"}]," constant. No single participant can accumulate an outsized fee discount."]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-abyss border border-edge/20 rounded-lg p-8","children":[["$","h4",null,{"className":"font-display text-star text-lg mb-3","children":"Ownership Renounced"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-dust text-sm leading-relaxed","children":["After deployment, contract ownership is ",["$","span",null,{"className":"text-chalk font-semibold","children":"permanently renounced"}]," via OpenZeppelin's ",["$","span",null,{"className":"text-chalk font-mono text-xs","children":"renounce_ownership()"}],". No admin functions can ever be called again — mint price, mint status, base URI, and admin minting are all permanently locked."]}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-abyss border border-star/20 rounded-lg p-8","children":[["$","h4",null,{"className":"font-display text-star text-lg mb-3","children":"Immutable Parameters"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-dust text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"After ownership is renounced, the following parameters are permanent and can never be modified 